STEPS OF SYSTEM INSTALLATION:


 Divide Partition

 Set time zone

 Create username and password
    
 Restart the system
    
 After OS Installed:

     Set proxy in system settings
     Deny Pendrive access  
     Update the softwares
     Restart the system


 Install following softwares :
     Iptux,
     Netbeans,
     Google-chrome,
     Lamp-server,
     Php5,
     Kdesvn,
     Phpmyadmin,
     Automatic shutdown.
     Apache configuration
     Create admin user
     Games removed
     Deny full rights to user
     
     
